-- 6. NOT REPRODUCIBLE HERE — MANUAL STEP
-- ---------------------------------------------------------------------
-- The Memories feature uploads photos to a PUBLIC Supabase Storage bucket
-- named `memories` (path pattern: {item.id}-{timestamp}.{ext}). Storage
-- buckets and their policies are not part of the table schema and cannot
-- be created by this file. On a fresh project you must, in the Supabase
-- dashboard:
--   1. Create a bucket named `memories`
--   2. Mark it Public
--   3. Add an INSERT policy with check (true)
-- Without this, memory photo uploads fail while the rest of the app works.
-- =====================================================================
